# 🎓 Wejheti

AI-powered university orientation assistant for Tunisian students.

## Features

- Predict suitable university programs
- Analyze Bac scores
- Machine Learning recommendation engine
- FastAPI backend
- Streamlit frontend

## Tech Stack

- Python
- Pandas
- Scikit-Learn
- FastAPI
- Streamlit

## Installation

```bash
git clone 
cd wejheti

pip install -r requirements.txt

uvicorn src.api.main:app --reload

streamlit run app/streamlit_app.py